Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚刚得到消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公要收留刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并且要把新野交给他驻军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们听着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备此人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}向来都是假称仁义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是他心怀大志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尤其他手下三员猛将
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽 张飞 赵云
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}个个是勇猛无比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们要严加防范哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.09,0:00:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 关张赵再是勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不过只带来两千多兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而我们有精兵数十万
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪怕一人吐口睡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也能将他生生淹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关羽三日之内连斩颜良文丑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连曹操对他都又敬又畏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们岂能轻视他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再者 刘备手下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然只有两千多兵勇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可个个是身经百战的老兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整日里吃酒赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有多少年没打仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发往新野的粮草军械
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都由我们供给
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们听着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发往新野的粮草军械
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定要两千人为度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多一点儿都不给他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以提防他扩充军备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军 主公夫人有请
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.25,0:01:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回禀夫人 我稍后就去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇叔请看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}翻过这座山就是新野城了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}新野城池虽不大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却是一座坚城
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}易守难攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}距襄阳也不过百里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如有战事 半日即可相援
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等能在新野驻脚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全亏了景升兄大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从踏入荆襄地界我就看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里 农田里稻谷丰盛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}村庄里人丁兴旺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与其他州郡相比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荆襄真是有天壤之别呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 父帅自领荆州后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就视荆襄为家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他甚至把自己的坟陵都选好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}准备终老于此处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 还有一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要多谢公子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我听孙乾说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他来拜见景升兄之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蔡瑁将军曾经极力反对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们入驻荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多亏了公子说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早晚有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会死于蔡瑁之手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇叔有所不知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我虽为长子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生母却不幸早亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅自领荆州后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另娶后母蔡氏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生下一子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是昨日你所看见的刘琮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘琮极受父帅的喜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蔡氏和她的弟弟蔡瑁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多年来一直在劝父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立刘琮为世子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蔡氏又是荆襄九郡最大的氏族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅大部分兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都掌握在上将军蔡瑁手里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说不定哪天夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就会死于非命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但如此 我甚至担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅百年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蔡瑁还会废了刘琮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自已做荆襄之主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可知道蔡瑁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何极力反对你来荆州吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是怕你坏了他的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}废长立幼 是取乱之道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}景升兄如此贤明 岂能不察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父帅年事已高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经管不住他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇叔 小侄想求你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子请吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请在父帅面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为我善言几句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}承景升兄大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才借得荆州一角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贵府的家事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}论理 我是断断不敢插嘴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}景升兄他征求我的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我定然会向他进谏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢皇叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我听说刘备来到咱们荆州了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公已准许他们驻扎新野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备手下是不是有几名悍将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}厉害得紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有三员悍将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们的名字叫关羽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞 赵云
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公已经六十四岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万一主公有个三长两短
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们荆州的这份家业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可不要落到别人手里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请姐姐放心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早有防备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备他们翻不了天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}除此之外 我还有一个心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐一直希望主公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能把二公子刘琮立为世子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过这心愿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还须从容行事才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是在意着点儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}千万别让刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}参与了咱们荆州的内政
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更不能让他跟刘琦抱成团了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}建安十一年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操再次击败袁绍残部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相继攻取冀 青 并 幽等州
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍于悲愤中吐血暴亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}至此 曹操取代袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成为大汉天地间最强盛的军阀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭请丞相入城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭请丞相入城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹孟德 曹阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若是没有我许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汝等可进得了这冀州城乎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是没有你许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们当然进不了冀州城啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}汝可不能忘了我的大功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然 先生的乌巢之功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等岂敢忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诸位 不要看这曹阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是如何的得意 威风凛凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当初那是跟我一块混日子的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我俩小的时候在一起偷鸡摸狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赌酒骗钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那段时光是何等的潇洒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何等的快活呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿瞒 我说的是也不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿瞒 曹阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿瞒到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 汝等快把曹阿瞒给我找来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生千万不可乱言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当心传到丞相耳朵里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大祸临头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么丞相不丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}阿瞒就是阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小混混一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟你和我都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个鼻子两个眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也难怪 尔等既非阿瞒故交
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又非读书之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安知这天下的逸闻趣事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 对了 阿瞒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有一个你我不及之长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贪色 贪色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且与众不同 了得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你我众所不及 独有其道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}匹夫 汝是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好生大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胆敢惊了我的坐骑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可知道我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我乃丞相故交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许子远是也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这么一个狗东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么也配姓许
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}配姓许
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去问问你家丞相曹阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若是没有我这个姓许的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尔等这帮匹夫粗汉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}安能进得了这冀州城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你再敢胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我砍了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尔等这些粗汉痴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}焉能知晓姓氏之来由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}名字之来历乎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要说你 匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把你家丞相叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不敬我一尺 也得让我三分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你不是就想要许攸这颗头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天姓许的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就把脖子给你伸在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}匹夫 有本事你就砍了去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到你家丞相阿瞒那儿去请功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}砍 有种的砍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}砍呀 谅你也没这个胆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}狗东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好一座雄伟壮丽的冀州府
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然比洛阳还稍胜一筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍拥有这等城池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实在是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿听说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍在建冀州时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有意要把它建成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下首府啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我现在算是明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么那些文人墨客
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都喜欢投奔袁绍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为他房子大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冀州这个地方先后出过四大名士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}包括陈琳等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陈琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是那个写讨贼檄文的陈琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立刻拿他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 陈琳押来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就是陈琳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你把我骂得惊天动地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山呼海啸 狗血淋头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫我听得好享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我就在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么不骂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人哪 骂是骂不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}誉满天下者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}往往也是毁满天下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看我这份气色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这份精神头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那都是叫人给骂出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我头痛发做 痛不可当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我读了你的讨贼檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的头痛立刻就好了 不药而愈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我有一事不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你骂我也就罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么要把
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操的祖宗三代都捎上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们与你何干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时候罪臣身为袁绍幕宾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受命撰写讨贼檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 不得不以笔为刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}痛下狠手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罪臣 请丞相赐罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以笔为刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂止是以笔做刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的一支笔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抵得上十万大军你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陈琳 起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当初我读你的大作的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就对你是又恨又气 又喜又爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天我坐在袁绍的大位上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自然对你是更要刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的才气是既逼人又喜人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今后 治政 驭民 青史丹书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都少不了你这样的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你要是不愿意做我的幕宾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就赏你一座宅子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二十匹绸缎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你尽可以关起门来吟风弄月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}写出了好诗文
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一个要送到我这儿让我欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要先睹为快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看可否
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相恩威浩荡 古今难觅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罪臣 愿意归降丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这就对了 这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}起来 起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:15:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你我之间 还骂出一份交情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我甚是快活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你先去吧 我们回头聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罪臣告退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是从袁绍内府中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}搜出来的书信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是谁写给袁绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲 这些大都是 这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直说无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这些都是我方的文武官吏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}写给袁绍的信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们早在建安初年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就暗通袁绍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不看了 看了生气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们拿着我们的傣禄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饱受着父亲的恩宠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暗地里却背主通贼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在罪证确凿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们只要依着姓名抓捕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们一个都跑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们自然是逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是抓住又能怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}斩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}斩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是不是应该把我也斩了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我也跟袁绍通过书信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我还拍过他的马屁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说他是南天一柱 万世楷模
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我况且如此更何况他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们是怕我们战败了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想给自个儿 留条后路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相明见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当年袁绍势力滔天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:18:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但仍非丞相对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如今袁绍命归九泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这区区书信更谈何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相不如烧此书简
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以示对老友相送
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看看荀彧是何等胸怀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相胸怀远大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下只是说了句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丕儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你把这些书信拿到正阳门外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当着文武百官的面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一把火焚尽并且告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既往之事 永不查究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚 你又闯祸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸在大庭广众之下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}侮辱主公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我令他住口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这小子竟然把头伸过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让我砍他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如我不砍他 我就成他孙子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一怒之下 就砍了这颗狗头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你把许攸砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸是我多年的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.22,0:21:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们破袁绍取冀州他立了头功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你把他砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我陪他一颗人头就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把许褚给我推出去斩首示众
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚他久经沙场 屡立战功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲饶恕他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军法难容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他砍了许攸更是天理难容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我把他推出去斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是一时冲动啊 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不是一时冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就要宰他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反了 反了 反了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我推出去 推出去 砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚确实有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但许攸在城关前狂妄叫嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下也是亲耳听到过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}的确辱丞相太甚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下建议 厚葬许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}表奏天子追封许攸为当阳侯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同时严惩许褚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令许褚在许攸坟前叩首认罪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.13,0:22:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸给咱们立了大功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们才刚刚进城
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就把他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下的人会怎么想我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们会觉得我心胸狭隘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人家刚说了我几句
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就着人把他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世人断不会这样揣想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为许攸满口胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实是无中生有 痴人说梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你怎么才能证明他是满口胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}痴人说梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下请才士们写篇奏文
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为丞相歌功颂德 驳斥许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}另外这片奏文
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就请陈琳来撰写是最为合适
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他的如椽之笔 堪称尚佳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文章奏成以后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定能象当年的讨贼檄文一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令海内外传诵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那要是陈琳清高 不愿意写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下前去拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当面说服陈琳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚 你杀了我多年好友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原本罪不可恕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我念你醉酒过失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.31,0:23:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就饶你不死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是从即日起 降为步卒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你去养马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有三个月之内
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不许喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.46,0:23:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你得去许攸的坟头给他磕头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.66,0:23:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快谢恩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快谢恩哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快谢恩哪 快呀 快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罪将谢恩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.95,0:24:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.95,0:24:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 多谢开言相救
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.63,0:24:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不必客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 刚才在堂上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.10,0:24:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一件事儿 让我好生糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.54,0:24:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有什么糊涂的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.24,0:24:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看啊 曹丕公子为我求情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.14,0:24:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这人都跪下了 主公就是不准
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.11,0:24:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是你一求情 主公就准了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.95,0:24:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.35,0:24:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}世子年轻 不知道哪句话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.09,0:24:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才能说到丞相的心里去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.59,0:24:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我老了 略知一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.93,0:25:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了 先生 你再替我求个情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.83,0:25:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你又惹什么祸了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有 喝酒的事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.78,0:25:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看主公让我当步卒 做马夫
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.54,0:25:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么都成 就连给那个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.21,0:25:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸磕一百个头我都认
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.92,0:25:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这不让喝酒 足足三个月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.65,0:25:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非把我憋死不可嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.63,0:25:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.63,0:25:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真是得寸进尺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.03,0:25:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个情啊 我不求
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.90,0:25:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别别 别别 别别
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.64,0:25:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生 救人救到底
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.37,0:25:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要是帮这大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.11,0:25:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚这辈子 都感谢你的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.31,0:25:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许褚啊 丞相的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.05,0:25:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么一点都不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.22,0:25:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么心思
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.76,0:26:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我告诉你 你是丞相最喜欢的战将
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.96,0:26:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你今天做了一件
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.46,0:26:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相想做而不敢做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.90,0:26:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀许攸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.07,0:26:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相气你是假 爱你才是真
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.81,0:26:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的 我怎么就没看出来呢你说
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.61,0:26:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要是看出来了你还是许褚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.05,0:26:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相之所以罚你去做马夫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.62,0:26:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之所以罚你禁酒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.62,0:26:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是为了磨炼你的性子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.13,0:26:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相想把你培养成为三军主将
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.61,0:26:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样 还让我替你去求情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.58,0:26:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不了 我 我喂马去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.44,0:27:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲请看 天下九州
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.71,0:27:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大半已收入父亲囊中
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.34,0:27:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在只剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.78,0:27:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘表 刘璋 孙策等辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.09,0:27:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘表啊 禄禄无为
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.49,0:27:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过是个守城之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.59,0:27:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荆州早晚是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.26,0:27:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘璋就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孙权 乳臭未干 兵少将寡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.91,0:27:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不足为虑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.01,0:28:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备呢 刘备在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.81,0:28:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 刘备投奔刘表之后
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.95,0:28:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已在小城新野驻军
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.62,0:28:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此城 地不到百里 兵不足三千
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.86,0:28:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因此就没标上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.89,0:28:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备不除 终是祸患
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.70,0:28:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲 袁绍死后 我们军势大振
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.97,0:28:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现有步军三十万 马军十五万
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.18,0:28:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水军二十万 总计六十五万
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.31,0:28:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其他各路诸侯加到一块儿
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.68,0:28:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不如我军的一半啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.62,0:28:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先让三军休整一年 厉兵秣马
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.79,0:28:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}储备粮草兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.09,0:28:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后 我要一鼓作气 一统天下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.85,0:29:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.22,0:29:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操掘开漳河 再次大破袁兵
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.76,0:29:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍气得吐血暴亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.67,0:29:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁谭 袁尚等公子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.27,0:29:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在大难临头时仍在争夺世子之位
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.21,0:29:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被曹操乘机猛攻
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.38,0:29:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后 几十万袁兵残部
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.68,0:29:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全部被曹操歼灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.08,0:29:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁氏二公子逃往辽东避难
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.89,0:29:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又被辽东太守公孙康斩杀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.19,0:30:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二袁首级被当做礼物 送往许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.40,0:30:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操陆续收取冀 青 并 幽各州
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.37,0:30:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大半个天下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.58,0:30:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都落入了曹操的贵囊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.25,0:30:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操声势滔天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.46,0:30:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 刘表传话来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.66,0:30:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要主公前往荆州 共渡端午佳节
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.77,0:30:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.08,0:30:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请问 阁下是刘皇叔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.18,0:30:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.25,0:30:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是蔡氏
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.39,0:31:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嫂夫人 在下失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.49,0:31:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不必多礼 荆州好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.33,0:31:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好 甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你就多待些日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.85,0:31:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此话何意
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.55,0:31:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫非是要撵我走
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.52,0:31:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇叔请进府吧 主公等候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.90,0:31:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊 你胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.01,0:31:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}气韵饱满 身形丰硕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.01,0:31:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.25,0:31:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下年近五十了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.38,0:32:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身无寸功 足无寸土
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.26,0:32:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有髀肉复生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.27,0:32:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}庸庸禄禄 日月蹉跎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.40,0:32:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老之将至啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.57,0:32:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.74,0:32:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还不满五十就感叹老之将至
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.45,0:32:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经六十有四 又当如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.49,0:32:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日请你来 是有一事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.59,0:32:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}隐忍多年 苦恼不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.50,0:32:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想请你为我一决
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.37,0:32:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请明公吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.18,0:33:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有两个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.15,0:33:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长子刘琦是前妻所生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.15,0:33:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人虽然贤良 却性格柔弱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.69,0:33:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难以托大业
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.63,0:33:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}次子刘琮是后妻蔡氏所生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.70,0:33:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}聪明伶俐 颇让我喜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.07,0:33:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蔡氏主掌内府
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.11,0:33:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其弟蔡瑁又是荆州的上将军
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.48,0:33:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他二人多次劝我废长立幼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.42,0:33:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让我好生为难哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.83,0:33:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公啊 你知道袁绍为何败亡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.93,0:34:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尽人皆知 袁绍是被曹操所败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.84,0:34:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}除了曹操善用兵外
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.88,0:34:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍另有内患
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.38,0:34:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就是他的三位公子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.25,0:34:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为世子之位相争不下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.45,0:34:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}临敌之际 甚至见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.49,0:34:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这才使得他大败于曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.86,0:34:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公 恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.30,0:34:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}废长立幼 自古便是取乱之道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.84,0:34:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更何况你已经说过 刘琦贤良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.74,0:34:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使 我有立刘琦之意
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.85,0:34:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但蔡氏一门荆州旺族 势盛力强
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.99,0:34:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们要不愿意 我怕激起内乱哪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.47,0:35:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公 今日端午佳节
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.87,0:35:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下敬你一盅
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.11,0:35:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}祝贵府家人和睦 荆州太平昌盛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.28,0:35:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊 今晚就不要回新野了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.42,0:35:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在客馆住下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.49,0:35:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日咱接着喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.14,0:35:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明公啊 刚才在屋内
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.78,0:35:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下不敢多言
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.41,0:35:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在容我斗胆说一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.78,0:35:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立世子之事 性命攸关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.52,0:35:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能明公一人做主
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.92,0:36:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}任何人不能僭越
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.26,0:36:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果明公忧虑蔡氏一门权重
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.93,0:36:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应该徐图削之
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.33,0:36:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}否则 谁为荆州之主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.14,0:36:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢明公美酒 在下暂且告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.85,0:36:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日相会
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.67,0:36:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.60,0:36:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有何话 起来说
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.84,0:36:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 贫妾害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.18,0:36:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.68,0:37:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}贫妾害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.55,0:37:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备会夺了你的荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.15,0:37:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会灭了我们蔡氏满门
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.79,0:37:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么会有这个念头
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.43,0:37:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备和刘琦已经抱成团了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.83,0:37:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备此次来荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.57,0:37:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是刘琦请来的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.93,0:37:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘琦想利用刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.54,0:37:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帮他立为世子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.14,0:37:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而刘备则想利用刘琦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.94,0:37:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帮他谋取荆州
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.31,0:37:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 如果不除掉刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.75,0:37:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕 早晚会大祸临头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.08,0:37:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.05,0:37:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 也许是贫妾多虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.72,0:37:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 请主公好生想想
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.99,0:37:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道贫妾所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.16,0:37:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就决无可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.40,0:37:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道他们
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就没有半点那样的念头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.37,0:37:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 就算是贫妾胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.81,0:38:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是请主公多多少少也提防着点
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.43,0:38:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐 你召我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.67,0:38:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二弟呀 再不动手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.70,0:38:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.87,0:38:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.58,0:38:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公今晚宴请刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.54,0:38:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只请了他一人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.08,0:38:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}席间 主公秘密向刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.85,0:38:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}征询立储的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.15,0:38:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.72,0:38:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}废长立幼 自古便是取乱之道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.52,0:38:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这厮好大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.66,0:38:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢干涉我荆州政事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.09,0:38:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他还跟主公说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.70,0:38:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍之所以兵败
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.43,0:38:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是因为诸子争大位
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.93,0:38:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}彼此见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.80,0:39:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由内乱导致败亡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.87,0:39:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你听听
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.34,0:39:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他这不是想趁乱谋取荆州吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.81,0:39:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人要是不除
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.55,0:39:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们蔡家马上就要大祸临头
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.52,0:39:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备现在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.09,0:39:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公让他今晚别回新野
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.09,0:39:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就住在客馆内
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.76,0:39:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我立刻调集人马
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.93,0:39:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁夜杀之 绝除后患
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.13,0:39:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后 我自去向主公请罪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.53,0:39:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二弟只管放手去做
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.97,0:39:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我料想 主公即便知道刘备被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.78,0:39:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然恼怒 却也不至于治你的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.65,0:39:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦 这是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.09,0:39:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你向主公请罪的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.72,0:39:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和刘琮也会跪在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.43,0:39:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起向他哭诉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.79,0:40:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而主公 他肯定心知肚明
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.23,0:40:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他知道荆州的军政大部
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.67,0:40:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}握于蔡氏之手 他即便是想杀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.61,0:40:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他既杀不动你 也杀不动我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.48,0:40:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更舍不得杀他的爱子刘琮
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.61,0:40:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更何况 他年事已高 别无所靠
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.18,0:40:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他只能依靠你我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.05,0:40:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来帮他维持荆州大业
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.49,0:40:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 他定会接受既成事实
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.83,0:40:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来 姐把一切都料理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.26,0:40:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这就去办
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.53,0:40:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一件事你必须当心
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.40,0:40:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是刘备手下的那些悍将们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.71,0:40:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.67,0:40:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那些人肯定是要为主子复仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.71,0:40:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关张赵虽然英勇
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.45,0:40:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我荆州将士也绝非庸手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.92,0:40:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们数十万人马
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.08,0:40:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道还灭不掉他两三千人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.39,0:40:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说了 刘备一死 群龙无首
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.26,0:40:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军心随之大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.32,0:41:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剿杀他们易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.29,0:41:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说得好 快去办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.96,0:41:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
